configuration.devTools.logFilter.mdDescr:
Developer Tools at extension webview log filter. You can filter by allowing or denying certain elements. Example:

```
{
  "allow": [
    { "level": "info" },
    { "tag": "component", "title": "AppProvider" },
    { "level": "info", "tag": "component", "title": "AppProvider" }
  ],
  "deny": [
    { "tag": "utils" }
  ]
}
```
